olone, Betamethasone, Fluorometholone, Methylprednisolone, Dexamethasone, Tetracycline, Minocycline, Miconazole, More', 'Mesoridazine, Methotrimeprazine, Asenapine, Perphenazine, Thiothixene, Pimavanserin, Lumateperone, Iloperidone, Triflupromazine, Loxapine, Molindone, More', 'Moderate', NULL, 'DDInter', 'pharmacodynamic', NULL, 'https://ddinter2.scbdd.com/server/interact/11464/', '[1] Cerner Multum, Inc. "UK Summary of Product Characteristics." O 0[2] Cerner Multum, Inc. "Australian Product Information." O 0', 1767369485);
